thread.title: Vote Leave 'cheating' may have affected Brexit result - Christopher Wylie

title: Vote Leave 'cheating' may have affected Brexit result - Christopher Wylie
text:
Vote Leave 'cheating' may have affected Brexit result - Christopher Wylie Tuesday, March 27, 2018 - 00:58 
Cambridge Analytica whistleblower Christopher Wylie tells British lawmakers that Vote Leave ''cheated'' during the EU referendum and that it could have swayed the result. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
